metadata.name: FAÇADE 01 - Hong Kong
metadata.description:
"Even though external circumstances may look dreadful, there is always something beautiful in you."

Mundane building facades from different cities become the medium through which various spectacles emerge.

This piece is the first of the 𝙁𝘼𝘾𝘼𝘿𝙀𝙎: 𝙄𝙣𝙣𝙚𝙧 𝘽𝙚𝙖𝙪𝙩𝙮 collection, every artwork is limited to an edition of one.
